{"tid":2291634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協等覆核挑戰防暴警及速龍小隊不展示警員編號勝訴","createTime":"2020-11-19T02:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T03:25:14.000Z","uid":277339,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2be5e93cf9343f90322987e67f7a2c5e82f6685c","tid":2291634,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"記協及多名市民就去年反修例示威期間，防暴警察及速龍小隊出勤時未有展示警員編號提出司法覆核，高等法院裁定記協、右眼受傷的男教師楊子俊，以及三名在示威中受傷的市叫陳恭信、魯湛思和吳康聯勝訴，裁定警務處處長無法有效確保每名「踏浪者」行動的警員，清晰展示警員編號，違反《香港人權法案》。 <br />\n<br />\n高等法院同時裁定，由投訴警察科處理警員投訴，並由監警會審視的投訴機制，不足以符合《香港人權法案》下，政府要建立獨立調查警員懷疑不當對待投訴機制的要求。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366922&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5oCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=7d52e80f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366922</a>"},{"pid":"b42446d74ec4576c03c8a6f433e0d02729201c07","tid":2291634,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"黑警態度照舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8eb1d0e28edd60217103f3b65261a9d2b5c50a6","tid":2291634,"uid":50386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:41:32.000Z","msg":"好快人大會出嚟廢埋香港人權法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05beccae5b07d2f3c6ec2858c49ca4e890db7fc","tid":2291634,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"閱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b5e49ff05cbf53f42ce5dc3aae603a7a059a7f","tid":2291634,"uid":284855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"高院會唔會犯国安法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e8877cd522ffbeb1ef5b03cb59a1960711d420","tid":2